<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p>Both legs of the REPO contract are transacted under one agreement. In the US the PSA agreement is often used, whilst in Europe the PSA/ISMA General Master Repo Agreement - GMRA - is often used. </p>
            <p>Standard agreement types should be entered onto this file, and referenced on the REPO contract in the field AGREEMENT.TYPE. </p>
        </ovdesc>
