<t>
<field>AGREEMENT.TYPE</field>
<desc>
            <p>The key to the agreement type. </p>
            <p>This information will be displayed on the REPO contract, and as such should be something meaningful that relates to the agreement type. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>A maximum of 8 characters may be entered.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>DESCRIPTION</field>
<desc>
            <p>The description of the agreement type. </p>
            <p>This description is used as the enrichment for the AGREEMENT.TYPE field in the REPO contract. </p>
            <p>This is a multi valued field. This is a sub valued language field. Standard T24 alphanumeric field. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>Mandatory input.</p>
            <p>A maximum of 35 characters may be entered.</p>
        </desc>
